# template-version: 2026-07.11
# Every variable the app needs, with safe placeholder values.
# Copy to .env and fill locally. NEVER commit .env (see .gitignore).
# App doesn't auto-load .env (many desktop/CLI stacks don't)? Then this
# file documents the REAL process env vars instead — and says so right
# here; an aspirational example the app never reads misleads agents.
# EXAMPLE_API_KEY=your-key-here
